   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="distribution">
      <p>
Distribution
</p>
      <p>
Circumglobal in subtropical and temperate waters. In the eastern Atlantic, it has been reported from the Arctic Seas (
Kramp 1938
) to 
South Africa
(Millard 1975). Its bathymetric range extends from the intertidal (Millard 1975) to depths of 
418 m
(
Gil &amp; Ramil 2017
) and 
451 m
(this paper).
</p>
